# Global Audit Memory

## Scope Touched
- `cauldrons/CauldronV4.sol` — primary hotspot across the audit; focus has centered on `cook()`, cached oracle/exchange-rate handling, `init()`, solvency enforcement, and liquidation-sensitive flows
